high_descs: Turn left and go toward the sink, to the left of the waste basket.
Pick up the bread from behind the sink.
Turn around, then turn left to go toward the stove.
Heat the bread in the microwave above the stove.
Turn around and go left, to the waste basket to the right of the sink.
Put the bread in the waste basket.
anns.task_desc: Put warm bread in the trash.

high_descs: Turn left and head towards the sink.
Pick up the bread on the counter.
Turn around and head towards the stove on your right.
Look up, open the microwave, heat up the bread, and take the bread out from it.
Turn around and head towards the gray bin next to the fridge on your left.
Place the bread in the bin.
anns.task_desc: Place the warm bread in the gray bin.

high_descs: Turn to the left and go to the sink.
Pick up the loaf of bread that is behind the sink.
Turn around.  Move to where the stove is and turn right to face the stove.
Open the door to the microwave.  Put the bread in the microwave and turn it on.  Open the door to the microwave and take the bread out.
Turn around and move towards the door.  Stop at the trash can.  Turn left to face the trash can.
Put the bread in the trash can.
anns.task_desc: Warm bread up to throw it in the trash.
